{"id":371,"date":"2014-03-23T19:52:01","date_gmt":"2014-03-23T23:52:01","guid":{"rendered":"http:\/\/rstp.fantomdesign.net\/?page_id=371"},"modified":"2020-06-10T09:52:09","modified_gmt":"2020-06-10T13:52:09","slug":"the-refugee-sponsorship-application-forms","status":"publish","type":"page","link":"https:\/\/www.rstp.ca\/en\/applications\/the-refugee-sponsorship-application-forms\/","title":{"rendered":"The Refugee Sponsorship Application Forms"},"content":{"rendered":"<p>All of the following forms must be completed, signed and dated and submitted together to the <a href=\"http:\/\/www.cic.gc.ca\/english\/resources\/publications\/ref-sponsor\/section-contact.asp\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Resettlement Operations Centre in Ottawa (ROC-O)<\/a> along with all required supporting documents.<\/p>\n<p>The <a href=\"http:\/\/www.cic.gc.ca\/english\/information\/applications\/private.asp\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Application for Refugee Sponsorship<\/a>\u00a0on IRCC&#8217;s website contains all the required forms, including those that must be completed and signed by the sponsoring group and the refugee applicant. The forms are also available to download below.<\/p>\n<p><strong>IMPORTANT<\/strong>: You must save or download the forms to your computer and open them using <a href=\"https:\/\/acrobat.adobe.com\/ca\/en\/acrobat.html\">Adobe Acrobat DC<\/a> or <a href=\"https:\/\/get.adobe.com\/reader\/\">Adobe Acrobat Reader DC<\/a>.<\/p>\n<p>Please\u00a0<a href=\"http:\/\/www.rstp.ca\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/How-to-download-the-PSR-forms.pdf\">click here<\/a>\u00a0for information on how to open the forms if you are experiencing problems.<\/p>\n<div class='content-column one_half'><div style=\"padding-right:20px;\"><h2>To be filled by the sponsoring group:<\/h2>\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><strong>For Sponsorship Agreement Holders<\/strong><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/www.canada.ca\/en\/immigration-refugees-citizenship\/services\/application\/application-forms-guides\/guide-sponsor-refugee-agreement-holder-constituent-group.html\">Use the guide<\/a>\u00a0to prepare and submit your application.<\/p>\n<p><strong>Forms for the sponsor<\/strong><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.canada.ca\/content\/dam\/ircc\/migration\/ircc\/english\/pdf\/kits\/forms\/imm5373e.pdf\">Sponsorship Undertaking \u2013 Sponsorship Agreement Holders (SAH) [IMM\u00a05373] (PDF, 1.56\u00a0MB)<\/a><\/li>\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.canada.ca\/content\/dam\/ircc\/migration\/ircc\/english\/pdf\/kits\/forms\/imm5440e.pdf\">Settlement Plan \u2014 Sponsorship Agreement Holders (SAH) [IMM\u00a05440] (PDF, 690\u00a0KB)<\/a><\/li>\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.canada.ca\/content\/dam\/ircc\/documents\/pdf\/english\/kits\/forms\/imm5492e.pdf\">Sponsor Assessment [IMM\u00a05492] (PDF, 664\u00a0KB)<\/a><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><strong>For Groups of Five<\/strong><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/www.canada.ca\/en\/immigration-refugees-citizenship\/services\/application\/application-forms-guides\/guide-sponsor-refugee-groups-five.html\">Use the guide<\/a> to prepare and submit your application<\/p>\n<p><strong>Forms for the sponsor<\/strong><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.canada.ca\/content\/dam\/ircc\/migration\/ircc\/english\/pdf\/kits\/forms\/imm5670e.pdf\">Sponsorship Undertaking and Settlement Plan \u2013 Groups of Five (G5) [IMM\u00a05670] (PDF,\u00a02.44\u00a0MB)<\/a><\/li>\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.canada.ca\/content\/dam\/ircc\/documents\/pdf\/english\/kits\/forms\/imm5492e.pdf\">Sponsor Assessment [IMM\u00a05492] (PDF, 664\u00a0KB)<\/a><\/li>\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.canada.ca\/content\/dam\/ircc\/migration\/ircc\/english\/pdf\/kits\/forms\/imm5373be.pdf\">Financial Profile [IMM\u00a05373B] (PDF,\u00a0101\u00a0KB)<\/a><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><strong>For Community Sponsors<\/strong><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/www.canada.ca\/en\/immigration-refugees-citizenship\/services\/application\/application-forms-guides\/guide-sponsor-refugee-community.html\">Use the guide<\/a>\u00a0to prepare and submit your application<\/p>\n<p><strong>Forms for the sponsor<\/strong><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.canada.ca\/content\/dam\/ircc\/migration\/ircc\/english\/pdf\/kits\/forms\/imm5663e.pdf\">Sponsorship Undertaking and Settlement Plan \u2013 Community Sponsor (CS) [IMM\u00a05663] (PDF,\u00a02.45\u00a0MB)<\/a><\/li>\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.canada.ca\/content\/dam\/ircc\/documents\/pdf\/english\/kits\/forms\/imm5492e.pdf\">Sponsor Assessment [IMM\u00a05492] (PDF, 664\u00a0KB)<\/a><\/li>\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.canada.ca\/content\/dam\/ircc\/migration\/ircc\/english\/pdf\/kits\/forms\/imm5373be.pdf\">Financial Profile [IMM\u00a05373B] (PDF, 651\u00a0KB)<\/a><\/li>\n<\/ul><\/div><\/div><div class='content-column one_half last_column'><h2>To be completed by the refugee applicant:<\/h2>\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/www.canada.ca\/en\/immigration-refugees-citizenship\/services\/application\/application-forms-guides\/guide-6000-convention-refugees-abroad-humanitarian-protected-persons-abroad.html\">Use the guide<\/a> to prepare and submit your application<\/p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><strong>Forms for the person being sponsored<\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.canada.ca\/content\/dam\/ircc\/migration\/ircc\/english\/pdf\/kits\/forms\/imm0008enu_2d.pdf\">Generic Application Form for Canada [IMM\u00a00008] (PDF, 731\u00a0KB)<\/a><\/li>\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.canada.ca\/content\/dam\/ircc\/migration\/ircc\/english\/pdf\/kits\/forms\/imm5669e.pdf\">Schedule A \u2013 Background\/Declaration [IMM\u00a05669] (PDF, 776\u00a0KB)<\/a><\/li>\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.canada.ca\/content\/dam\/ircc\/migration\/ircc\/english\/pdf\/kits\/forms\/imm0008_2e.pdf\">Schedule 2: Refugees Outside Canada [IMM\u00a00008\/Schedule 2] (PDF, 2.13\u00a0MB)<\/a><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><strong>Optional forms<\/strong><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.canada.ca\/content\/dam\/ircc\/migration\/ircc\/english\/pdf\/kits\/forms\/imm5476e.pdf\">Use of a Representative [IMM\u00a05476] (PDF, 648\u00a0KB)<\/a><\/li>\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.canada.ca\/content\/dam\/ircc\/migration\/ircc\/english\/pdf\/kits\/forms\/imm5956e.pdf\">Appointment of Representative(s) in Expected Community of Settlement [IMM\u00a05956] (PDF,\u00a0138\u00a0KB)<\/a><\/li>\n<\/ul><\/div><div class='clear_column'><\/div><\/p>\n<h2>Other forms:<\/h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.canada.ca\/content\/dam\/ircc\/migration\/ircc\/english\/pdf\/kits\/forms\/imm5438e.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Request for Refugee Profile [IMM5438]<\/a><\/li>\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.canada.ca\/en\/immigration-refugees-citizenship\/services\/application\/application-forms-guides\/application-refugee-sponsorship-joint-assistance-sponsorship.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Application for Refugee Sponsorship: Joint Assistance Sponsorship<\/a><\/li>\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.canada.ca\/en\/immigration-refugees-citizenship\/services\/application\/application-forms-guides\/request-process-family-members-under-year-window-opportunity-provisions.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Request to process overseas family members under one-year window of opportunity provision<\/a><\/li>\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.canada.ca\/content\/dam\/ircc\/migration\/ircc\/english\/pdf\/kits\/forms\/imm5618e.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Request to add a family member to a private sponsorship undertaking [IMM 5618]<\/a><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><strong>Note<\/strong><\/span><br \/>\n<strong>*\u00a0<\/strong>As a Group of Five, you must make sure that you submit a <strong>Financial Profile form<\/strong>\u00a0for each group member who is\u00a0contributing financially and a <strong>Sponsor Assessment<\/strong> form for each member.<\/p>\n","